{"tid":234596,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本《素人之亂》作者聲援！ 籲救救Hidden Agenda","createTime":"2017-05-08T11:57:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-08T15:23:36.000Z","uid":20933,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6de2b1f5a4b5aff1a643d42fc7dad4741a2c4ced","tid":234596,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T11:57:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170508/large/1494230042_b411.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170508%2Flarge%2F1494230042_b411.jpg&h=76e3fe00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n多次被逼遷的音樂表演場地Hidden Agenda（HA），昨晚邀請英國樂隊在觀塘鴻圖道一工廠大廈單位內表演時，懷疑樂隊沒有按法例申請工作簽證，遭入境處人員放蛇冚檔，爆發衝突，日本著名左翼社運人士、《素人之亂》作者松本哉今日在其網誌發表題為《香港Hidden Agendaを救え》的文章，向日本讀者詳述HA事件。<br />\n<br />\n他在文中上載事發影片和HA日常演出片段，直言「非法」經營是無可奈何，對於HA被指聘請黑工，松本哉認為指控荒謬，他說若過於謹守規則，不只音樂表演，其他如展覽等活動都將無法舉行，「世界將會變得無聊」。他又指香港租金比東京貴兩三倍，要在一般商業場所經營音樂場地，幾乎不可能，他認為世界大多情況充滿灰色地帶，認為香港政府今次以違法為由作出拘捕行動並不合理，呼籲大家捍衛這個香港獨立音樂場所。<br />\n<br />\n日本311大地震後，發動日本最大規模反核運動的松本哉，就是「素人之亂」的代表人物，他本來是個普通人，在高圓寺一間叫「素人之亂」的二手店當店長，深感社會不公義，常常發起抗議，但響應的人有限，直至反核示威，忽然間過萬群眾響應，令主流媒體震驚。"},{"pid":"9bbecba84857bfa0cccf6f661170dcadfee09c42","tid":234596,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T11:57:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170508&amp;guid=56666331&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170508%26guid%3D56666331%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant&d=WZfMoUUHHVTN90V%2FD%2BJOGQtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=f4fc227b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170508%26guid%3D56666331%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant&h=eda8ae48\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170508&amp;guid=56666331&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant</a>"},{"pid":"5dd7ad1cf3d7f8ad8bdccf97a06eed2d9e09f4a5","tid":234596,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T12:00:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://ameblo.jp/tsukiji14/entry-12272793802.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fameblo.jp%2Ftsukiji14%2Fentry-12272793802.html&d=WZfMoUUHHVTN90V%2FD%2BJOGQtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=afc1f8f7\" target=\"_blank\">http://ameblo.jp/tsukiji14/entry-12272793802.html</a>"},{"pid":"2d25be9140f55197969a4566d7b84ba24e9a3e08","tid":234596,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T12:03:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e17e2a2f402bf4490ae7124753ca4776620f87c5","tid":234596,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T12:06:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"042a7868bf303f555ced58f26c08448d10c78452","tid":234596,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T15:14:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c682628a36cdc305f1eb1c463492900037e7d2dd","tid":234596,"uid":46688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T15:23:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}